{"tid":2129408,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【留家抗疫】一個人可以幾耐唔出街？研究：呢個年紀最唔忍得","createTime":"2020-07-28T14:35:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-28T15:04:04.000Z","uid":166360,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"347869e1ffd0f907e24546e53583040c54040e68","tid":2129408,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T14:35:11.000Z","msg":"【留家抗疫】一個人可以幾耐唔出街？研究：呢個年紀最唔忍得<br />\n親子 撰文：鄧煥儀 2020-07-28 21:00<br />\n<br />\n&quot;40歲人士最唔忍得<br />\n<br />\n日本內閣府去年針對流感疫情，向18歲或以上的民眾進行調查，看看人們為了限制疾病傳播，可接受多長時間的自我隔離。在收回的1473份答覆之中，36.9%的人能一星期不出門，18.9%的人能忍受兩星期，15.4%的人僅能忍受2至3天。<br />\n<br />\n日本野村證券根據這項數據進行加權計算，發現平均一個人可接受14.4天不外出進行實體社交活動，當中不同年紀的人存有分別。40歲左右的人能忍受的時間最短，為12天；70歲以上者能忍受的時間最長，為18天。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E8%A6%AA%E5%AD%90/503705/%E7%95%99%E5%AE%B6%E6%8A%97%E7%96%AB-%E4%B8%80%E5%80%8B%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E5%B9%BE%E8%80%90%E5%94%94%E5%87%BA%E8%A1%97-%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6-%E5%91%A2%E5%80%8B%E5%B9%B4%E7%B4%80%E6%9C%80%E5%94%94%E5%BF%8D%E5%BE%97\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E8%25A6%25AA%25E5%25AD%2590%2F503705%2F%25E7%2595%2599%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E6%258A%2597%25E7%2596%25AB-%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%2580%258B%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%258F%25AF%25E4%25BB%25A5%25E5%25B9%25BE%25E8%2580%2590%25E5%2594%2594%25E5%2587%25BA%25E8%25A1%2597-%25E7%25A0%2594%25E7%25A9%25B6-%25E5%2591%25A2%25E5%2580%258B%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E7%25B4%2580%25E6%259C%2580%25E5%2594%2594%25E5%25BF%258D%25E5%25BE%2597&d=jpV%2F2%2Bss%2F2Wq3uOsKpdaDyLieoVo5Z%2Bt8AyiqwqBN0Y%3D&h=ef054e4b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E8%A6%AA%E5%AD%90/503705/%E7%95%99%E5%AE%B6%E6%8A%97%E7%96%AB-%E4%B8%80%E5%80%8B%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E5%B9%BE%E8%80%90%E5%94%94%E5%87%BA%E8%A1%97-%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6-%E5%91%A2%E5%80%8B%E5%B9%B4%E7%B4%80%E6%9C%80%E5%94%94%E5%BF%8D%E5%BE%97</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">毒撚唔出街幾個月都絕對無難度</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14fa8f3a95c17eedf8264eb3a57b13cdf2fde7a8","tid":2129408,"uid":20241,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T14:54:29.000Z","msg":"有網上有外賣我成年唔出街都仲得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9476e77373e7ce623680cfce1d9cbcdae4c0762c","tid":2129408,"uid":104138,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"347869e1ffd0f907e24546e53583040c54040e68","tid":2129408,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T14:35:11.000Z","msg":"【留家抗疫】一個人可以幾耐唔出街？研究：呢個年紀最唔忍得<br />\n親子 撰文：鄧煥儀 2020-07-28 21:00<br />\n<br />\n&quot;40歲人士最唔忍得<br />\n<br />\n日本內閣府去年針對流感疫情，向18歲或以上的民眾進行調查，看看人們為了限制疾病傳播，可接受多長時間的自我隔離。在收回的1473份答覆之中，36.9%的人能一星期不出門，18.9%的人能忍受兩星期，15.4%的人僅能忍受2至3天。<br />\n<br />\n日本野村證券根據這項數據進行加權計算，發現平均一個人可接受14.4天不外出進行實體社交活動，當中不同年紀的人存有分別。40歲左右的人能忍受的時間最短，為12天；70歲以上者能忍受的時間最長，為18天。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E8%A6%AA%E5%AD%90/503705/%E7%95%99%E5%AE%B6%E6%8A%97%E7%96%AB-%E4%B8%80%E5%80%8B%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E5%B9%BE%E8%80%90%E5%94%94%E5%87%BA%E8%A1%97-%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6-%E5%91%A2%E5%80%8B%E5%B9%B4%E7%B4%80%E6%9C%80%E5%94%94%E5%BF%8D%E5%BE%97\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E8%25A6%25AA%25E5%25AD%2590%2F503705%2F%25E7%2595%2599%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E6%258A%2597%25E7%2596%25AB-%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%2580%258B%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%258F%25AF%25E4%25BB%25A5%25E5%25B9%25BE%25E8%2580%2590%25E5%2594%2594%25E5%2587%25BA%25E8%25A1%2597-%25E7%25A0%2594%25E7%25A9%25B6-%25E5%2591%25A2%25E5%2580%258B%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E7%25B4%2580%25E6%259C%2580%25E5%2594%2594%25E5%25BF%258D%25E5%25BE%2597&d=jpV%2F2%2Bss%2F2Wq3uOsKpdaDyLieoVo5Z%2Bt8AyiqwqBN0Y%3D&h=ef054e4b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E8%A6%AA%E5%AD%90/503705/%E7%95%99%E5%AE%B6%E6%8A%97%E7%96%AB-%E4%B8%80%E5%80%8B%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E5%B9%BE%E8%80%90%E5%94%94%E5%87%BA%E8%A1%97-%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6-%E5%91%A2%E5